  "instructions": [
    "Heat peanut oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onions, garlic, and green bell peppers; sauté for about 5 minutes until softened.",
    "Add sun-dried tomatoes and continue to cook for an additional minute.",
    "Fold in vegan mozzarella cheese and gently stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Drizzle with pomegranate molasses, add birds-eye chili flakes, and lemon juice. Stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Transfer the dish onto a plate or platter and garnish with sesame seeds if desired.",
    "Serve hot as a main course."
